{"tid":1971673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［泰國人報仇］中國被指是湄公河大旱元兇　築壩儲水無視泰國等下遊國家","createTime":"2020-04-14T05:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T08:44:20.000Z","uid":105567,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69fc8f1f8aa3c5b9fdb2a8d451e9c99848a9ccb9","tid":1971673,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"全長 4,350 公里的湄公河流經中國雲南省、泰國、緬甸、老撾等多個國家，滋養近 6,000 萬人。但據路透社報道，中國在湄公河上流建有 11 個堤霸，但在去年下遊出現乾旱之際沒有放水，或是去年下遊流域遇上 50 年一遇大乾旱的原因。<br />\n<br />\n去年，湄公河的下遊流域出現嚴重乾旱，農夫和漁民甚至能看到因河水不足而露出的土地。據衛星照片分析，下遊的水位較正常時下降了近 3 米。與此同時，在中國雲南省，亦即是湄公河的上遊位置，5 月至 10 月的雨季間，可量度到其水位輕微高於水平。<br />\n<br />\n跟進湄公河狀況的美國研究組織「Eyes on Earth」認為，中國「在雨季時不讓水源流向下遊」，又指中國的限制會嚴重影響下遊的生態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%B9%84%E5%85%AC%E6%B2%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B1%E5%85%83%E5%85%87-%E7%AF%89%E5%A3%A9%E5%84%B2%E6%B0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25B9%2584%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2597%25B1%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2585%2587-%25E7%25AF%2589%25E5%25A3%25A9%25E5%2584%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8yPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ef84a917\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25B9%2584%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2597%25B1%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2585%2587-%25E7%25AF%2589%25E5%25A3%25A9%25E5%2584%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=27cb4c9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%B9%84%E5%85%AC%E6%B2%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B1%E5%85%83%E5%85%87-%E7%AF%89%E5%A3%A9%E5%84%B2%E6%B0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a>"},{"pid":"ad545d6c75282c610d51fe12a44b7a43805de086","tid":1971673,"uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"中國在河流上遊設有 11 個堤霸，但一直沒有公開儲水數字，Eyes on Earth 則指，中國儲水逾 47 億立方米。中方則已承諾，願意在河流管理上合作，並且將調查去年乾旱的成因。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部則回覆路透社，指中國堤壩令下遊乾旱的說法不合理 (unreasonable) 。外交部又指，去年雲南省出現嚴重乾旱，河水水位亦下降至歷史新低，因此要在堤壩儲存水量。該回覆中，中國使用的字眼是瀾滄江而非湄公河，亦即是中國國內稱呼湄公河的名字。"},{"pid":"e5801b1c225850459f3b28e7cf588b1b02e4e9f1","tid":1971673,"uid":241804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:36:22.000Z","msg":"cls, 癲撚到斷人水路，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a51c94689edf5562c4c35ae7b9855e2a71c522","tid":1971673,"uid":44171,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"N年前又講係戰爭行為黎， 幾時打過？"},{"pid":"2fd663316dd55567b928ef5f63007449a13987aa","tid":1971673,"uid":9542,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"去年雲南省出現嚴重乾旱，河水水位亦下降至歷史新低，因此要在堤壩儲存水量<br />\n<br />\n咪即係認左唔放水囉屌你老母支那人"},{"pid":"de8322676f23baa7652a678e655898801cdf90f7","tid":1971673,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:3